<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>لوحة تحكم المستخدم | بلسم</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 p-6">
    <header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">مرحباً يا ياسين</h1>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a href="profile.html" class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-slate-200">الملف الشخصي</a>
